---
source: tests/setup.rs
expression: "plan_output(&[\"setup\", \"--plan\"])"
---
hpds setup --profile dev runs these 8 steps:
  1. r
       hpds install r
  2. quarto
       hpds install quarto
  3. uv
       hpds install uv
  4. gh
       hpds install gh
  5. rig
       hpds install rig
  6. tinytex
       hpds install tinytex
  7. togi
       hpds install togi
  8. git setup
       hpds git setup
